𝐃𝐢𝐠𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐁𝐚𝐬𝐢𝐜𝐬 is the practice of promoting products or services through digital channels, such as the internet, social media, email, mobile apps, and other digital technologies. It is a rapidly growing field that offers businesses of all sizes a cost-effective and efficient way to reach their target audience and increase their visibility in the online marketplace. In order to create an effective digital media marketing strategy, businesses must first identify their target audience and understand their needs and preferences.
